description:
The Great Sorting: Red gets redder, blue gets bluer. George Floyd statue vandalized in New York. What would Biden do if the Chinese took Taiwan. Prediction: Fauci will demand boosters for everyone. Twitter labels woman's obituary misleading because it said she died as result of vaccine. Massachusetts covid spike, almost a third hospitalized are fully vaccinated.
